oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Main Street in Erwin
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Main Street looking southwest from the intersection of Gay and Main Streets. People are standing on the sidewalk and in the dirt road. The building on the left corner is a bank.
